Eu e Johnny Dogs.

619
00:45:39,440 --> 00:45:41,840
São você e Johnny Dogs contra a Escócia.

620
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:46,120
Lá na BSA,

621
00:45:46,200 --> 00:45:48,600
