00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:50,360
Sem ela, não passa de peso morto.

643
00:47:15,520 --> 00:47:17,680
São eles, os Billy Boys.

644
00:47:38,720 --> 00:47:39,600
Cavalheiros,

645
00:47:40,600 --> 00:47:45,480
